        <Parent_String>flat-woven [300245805], textile weaving processes and techniques [300245451], textile construction processes and techniques [300239729], textile processes and techniques [300239669], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
